chunks.html_content:
Register cattle births and report cattle deaths and movements. See details of your herd and individual animals and make sure your records match those on CTS Online.

New users need to register on CTS Online.

CTS Online does not work on old operating systems or browsers, including:

  • Windows XP
  • Windows Vista
  • Internet Explorer 6
  • Internet Explorer 7

You can check the compatibility of your operating system and internet browser.

You’ll need to upgrade your system to use CTS Online.

You can contact the British Cattle Movement Service (BCMS) Helpline.
